title: Bech Senior Bowl MVP month after brother's death
description: TCU receiver Jack Bech was selected MVP of the Senior Bowl on Saturday, catching the winning touchdown pass a month after his brother died in the deadly pickup truck attack in New Orleans.

title: Hurley says Arizona had 'no class' in testy finish
description: Arizona State coach Bobby Hurley said Arizona had "no class" in the Wildcats' win Saturday after trash talk led to a Sun Devils player head-butting Wildcats star Caleb Love.

title: Borthwick's bold plan crumbles to dust in Dublin
description: England's hopes of emulating 2019's shock win in Dublin were dashed by errors and their enduring habit of fading out of second halves.

title: Jones hat-trick gives Scotland nervy win over Italy
description: A Huw Jones hat-trick gets Scotland off to a winning start in a nervy Six Nations opener against Italy at Murrayfield.

title: Clippers, Jazz reportedly pull off a pretty big deal
description: Los Angeles is trading PJ Tucker and Mo Bamba to the Jazz for Drew Eubanks and Patty Mills.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: No. 11 Kansas blows its biggest lead ever in 81-70 loss to Baylor
description: Kansas led by 21 in the first half and by 19 at halftime.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: Liverpool look unstoppable as Hurzeler shows his inexperience
Azim hammers former champion Lipinets to seize stoppage victory
description: Adam Azim scored a dominant victory over Sergey Lipinets to win their Wembley Arena clash inside nine rounds.
